<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-chances-a-chance">take chances / a chance</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>冒险一试；碰运气：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She taught me to take chances and not be afraid. 
她教导我要敢于冒险一试，不要害怕。</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m not sure of beating him, but let me take a chance. 
我虽没有把握打败他，但还是要碰碰运气。</p></div></div>